original_title: Aisha Tyler Is Lit: Live at the Fillmore
overview: Uncut, uncensored, and unapologetic, Aisha Tyler brings her outrageous wit to the topics we really care about: from bikini waxes and breast implants to online porn, strip clubs, sexual positions and what your gay friends really think, nothing is off-limits!
